{"tid":586892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"博通若成功購高通 英特爾傳或研購合併後公司","createTime":"2018-03-10T03:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T03:21:53.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1e75481f8f459fe5b608cb5103faa983e89c05ae","tid":586892,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T03:21:53.000Z","msg":"《華爾街日報》引述消息人士稱，倘若博通(Broadcom)成功收購高通(Qualcomm)，英特爾(Intel)考慮向對方提出收購建議。<br />\n<br />\n英特爾是全球最大晶片生產商，也是視博通及高通的合併，將對該公司產生很大威脅。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士指出，這也是英特爾考慮，一旦博通與高通合併，便考慮向對方提出收購的理由。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/international/article/1786405\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2FinstantnewsMob%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F1786405&d=w%2FJJPWM%2FuT9sStkqp369R9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=af103c76\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/international/article/1786405</a><br />\n<br />\n螳螂捕蟬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}